structure.unit: ARTICLE XL. KENDALL TAMIAMI EXECUTIVE AIRPORT ZONING

text.section:
Sec. 33-405. Conflicting regulations.
Nothing contained in this article shall be interpreted to conflict with or supersede any federal regulation pertaining to the control of hazards to air navigation; provided however, where this article imposes lower height limitations or more stringent restrictions upon the use of land or water than are imposed or required by other County ordinance or resolution, or federal rules or regulations the provisions of this article shall govern.
